          class="projects__description lg:text-xl to-be-scrolled max-w-3xl text-center pt-2 px-8 lg:pt-8 lg:pb-20"
          id="projectsDescription"
        >
          From the concept, the design, the development, and the deployment.<br
          />
          The following is a selection of projects I've worked on.
        </div>
        <Projects client:load />
        <div
          class="circle-of-development--container to-be-scrolled min-h-[80vh] lg:min-h-0 my-12 hidden"
        >
