                aria-hidden="true"
              />
              <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold">
                <span id="lifelongLearner">Lifelong learner</span>
              </h3>
              <p id="lifelongLearner__content" class="lg:text-lg">
                Graduated in Software Development career. I always try to learn
                new things and experiment with new technologies. It's the best
                way to keep up with the fast-paced world. Not everything I learn
                is related to programming. Astronomy and Aerial Robotics are
                topics that I love to learn about.
              </p>
              <div class="about-me-container-links">
                <a
                  href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/marcelo-arias/details/certifications/"
