                  <i class="fas fa-award" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  <span id="onlineCertifications">Online certifications</span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-me-container__box">
            <div class="box__description-container">
              <img
                src="./images/separator.svg"
                width={0}
                alt=""
                class="about-me-separator"
                aria-hidden="true"
              />
              <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold">
                <span id="lifelongLearner">
                  Rise of Artificial Intelligence
                </span>
              </h3>
              <p id="lifelongLearner__content" class="lg:text-lg">
                In the rise of Artificial Intelligence, I joined SmartUp AI, a
                start-up that powers the future of communication and
                collaboration with AI. I worked on the design, development,
                research, and deployment of the platform. SmartUp AI was
                recognized in 2023 as one of the top AI-native startups in Latin
                America.
              </p>
              <div class="about-me-container-links">
                <a
                  href="https://www.smartup.lat"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noreferrer"
                >
                  <i class="fas fa-rocket" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  <span id="onlineCertifications">SmartUp</span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-me-container__box">
            <div class="box__description-container">
              <img
