      </p>
      <p class="footer__description" id="madeWith">
        Marcelo Arias is a Software Engineer.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer__row">
      <p class="footer__email">hello@marceloarias.com</p>
      <p>2015 - 2023</p>
    </div>
